    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Step into luxury with this stunning vehicle in absolute mint condition! It truly looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor, with a flawless interior and a gleaming exterior that has been meticulously maintained. This is a rare chance to own a car that is essentially brand new and ready for its next adventure!",
